W: Oh, I see. [Pause] Here you are.
M: Thank you. How much is it?
W: It’s ten dollars. If you are interested in this
book, why don’t you buy the whole series?
M: How many books are there?
W: There are four books, and the price of each
book is the same.
M: Can I get a discount if I buy the whole
series?
W: Yes. You can get a ten percent discount.
M: Terrific. I’ll buy the whole series.
discount 할인
terrific 멋진
